  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L50\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts#L10-L50\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/testing\", \"name\": \"@angular/core/testing\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/testing/async\", \"name\": \"async\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/core/testing\">@angular/core/testing</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"async\">async<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/async#async\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Wraps a test function in an asynchronous test zone. The test will automatically\ncomplete when all asynchronous calls within this zone are done. Can be used\nto wrap an <a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\"><code>inject</code></a> call.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">把一个测试函数包装进一个异步测试区域（Zone）。当该区域中的所有异步调用都已完成时，该测试将会自动完成。\n可用于包装 <a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\"><code>inject</code></a> 调用。</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>(fn: Function): (<a href=\"api/core/ApplicationInitStatus#done\" class=\"code-anchor\">done</a>: any) => any</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>fn</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>Function</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>(<a href=\"api/core/ApplicationInitStatus#done\" class=\"code-anchor\">done</a>: any) => any</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/async#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">Example:</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">例子：</p>\n<code-example>\nit('...', <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>(inject([AClass], (object) => {\n  object.doSomething.then(() => {\n    expect(...);\n  })\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/AsyncPipe\n - api/common/NgForOf\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - api/core/testing/tick\n - api/core/testing/withBody\n - api/http/testing/MockBackend\n - guide/http\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/reactive-forms\n - guide/router\n - guide/rx-library\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n - tutorial/toh-pt6\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/ApplicationInitStatus#done\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/async#async\n - api/core/testing/async#description\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L50\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts#L10-L50\n-->"
